          "text": "咱不是鬼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是大王？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱也不是大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人，站在我家房上？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱乃大王的奶奶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我却不信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊一声夫人休要吓，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（叫） 哇呀哇呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅花娘下桌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奴家乃是女豪侠。\n身上现出绣花袄。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（叫） 哇呀哇呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母、朱小姐",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，饶命吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "唬得他母女乱如麻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "迈动金莲摆几摆、朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，你还有嘴上呢……"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "嘴上胡须不要它。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，原来是位大娘。请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有坐。吓夫人，小姐因何欲寻短见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大娘有所不知，只因花光贼子，讹我老爷在日，借了他家一万两银子。如今本\n利全要，大约十万有余。有了银子便罢，如若不然，要将我家宝贝锁云囊，同\n着女儿抬过府去，抵押此款。乞求大人作主！"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。花公子之父在朝为官，这门亲事，可以允得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大娘，我女乃窈窕之体，岂肯配那蠢郎为妻么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，原来如此，请小姐退下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿且退下。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱小姐允，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，我替小姐前去如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家为难之事，怎好劳动大娘？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你代吾女前去，只恐难出花府。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人放心。我既有进路，定有出路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我母女哪里安身？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人不嫌，到我家中暂住，再作道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎好补报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不必过谦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知从哪条路去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前面大街，见有红灯一盏，便是我家。用手敲门，定有人来开门，不要害怕于\n他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "知道了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小锣。梅花娘换衣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，现有包裹一个，吩咐他家人来，不许开看。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花府来人呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（花院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家小姐，有包裹一个，不许开看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "文契呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在这里。叫他们搭轿上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搭轿上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。四青袍、轿夫同上，梅花娘坐轿，同下。朱小姐上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家院。我与小姐往邻居家住，尔等在家看守门户。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱院允，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，随我来罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是，有红灯一盏，待我叫门。\n有人么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梁上君上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们哪里来的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梅花娘叫我们来的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，他叫你们来的，进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如今梅花娘哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "被花府抢去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "被花府抢去了？哦，想她认得路径，必然回来，进去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱母、朱小姐同允，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我想梅花娘此去，莫说物件，连人都盗了两个来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梁上君下。）"
        }
      ],
