    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "一霎时浑身软眉头锁紧",
        "众人",
        "四下手",
        "梅花娘",
        "花光",
        "花院"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（花光上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两朵金花插两旁，今日打扮做新郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（花院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷，花轿到了，宝贝也来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐搭上堂来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搭上堂来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。四青袍、轿夫、梅花娘同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一块沉香木，雕成一马鞍。新贵来上跨，四季永平安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请新人交拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。梅花娘、花光交拜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜大爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下面领赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同允，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐前日亮的什么宝贝？取出与卑人一看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公欲看此宝，须要取枝御香。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御香在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我焚香。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "顿然间绣房内香风阵阵，\n锁云囊果然是价值千金。\n昏沉沉倒椅上气喘吁吁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "一霎时浑身软眉头锁紧、梅花娘",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这狂徒顿然间昏迷不醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅花娘与花光换衣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "俺这里换行装混出府门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，这贼子将门闭起，如何是好。哦，有了。\n呔！府中有了强盗！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四下手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿强盗！拿强盗！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅花娘混下。花院上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要打，不要打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四下手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是大爷醉倒在此，看解药来。大爷醒来，大爷醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，小姐吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人们在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！你们这些狗头，怎么跑到绣房来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷你头上？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，贼帽子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身上？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼衣裳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有嘴上？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是贼胡子！小姐呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不见了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宝贝呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不见了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若朱夫人，问我要小姐宝贝，拿何言答对？"
        },
        {
          "character": "花院",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷做张状纸，当堂去告。追着宝贝，就有小姐的下落。"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。速去办来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（花院允。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花光",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，强盗吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
