    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众人",
        "朱母",
        "梁上君",
        "梅公子",
        "梅花娘"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅花娘上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梁上君上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大娘请进。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大郎，可有个老夫人带一小姐到此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梁上君",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的。\n老夫人请出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（朱母上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大娘回来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人请坐。请问令爱可曾许配与人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无有门当户对。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胞弟人才出众，不知夫人意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（梅公子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姐姐何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见过夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然人才出众。愿将小女许配令弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过来谢过岳母。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。岳母请上，受小婿一拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。这有宝贝锁云囊，你带至京中，文章得中便罢，如若不然，即将此宝献\n上皇家，也能得一官半职。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢岳母。姐姐将此宝打在行李之内。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岳母请上，小婿拜别。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。梅公子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我母女回去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人回去不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那贼一计不成，二计又来，待我夫妻保你逃往苏州去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此甚好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "梅花娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，天已明了，赶路要紧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖尾声〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
